snippet.title: World of Sea Battle. Gameplay Trailer #2
snippet.description:
Welcome to World of Sea Battle!
Go from a simple sailor to a formidable sea wolf, join a guild or fight alone! An open game world that can accommodate thousands of players, fierce battles, politics and trade, dozens of types of ships, your own personal island and much more awaits you in the MMORPG World of Sea Battle!
World of Sea Battle, registration in the game and download: https://www.worldofseabattle.com/
Our VK group: https://vk.com/worldofseabattle
Join the ever growing Discord gaming community: https://discord.com/invite/Qvxmj3BA3q
Subscribe to our channel and participate in the life of the game: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMllqFqcAx_e8HWSYxG7xJg?sub_confirmation=1
